list.comment: If I’ve said it once, I’ve said it a million times: I DIDN’T SAVE @thefancykerr, SHE SAVED ME 🐶🐶🐶It’s true that a dog can change your life: A four legged friend can put a smile on your face, pull you out of depression, & create a selfless love that you never knew existed 😍😍😍// In honor of #GivingTuesday, I will personally donate $1 to @dognkittycity, The Humane Society of Dallas County (where I adopted her from) for every comment this post receives by MIDNIGHT tonight! #KERRentlyGivingBack // How are you helping your community today?!

Finally feeling like myself again after being SICKER THAN A DOG since last Thursday 😬😬😬// During my sniffing, snorting, coughing, & wheezing...I realized that when you say YES to everyone & everything by trying to do it all, you actually end up saying NO to yourself...and for me, that resulted in running down my body & getting sick 🤦🏼‍♀️🤦🏼‍♀️🤦🏼‍♀️// So consider this your friendly reminder that it’s okay to put yourself first every now & then if it means sacrificing your wellness & your health! // IN OTHER NEWS, I’m feeling VERY THIN after being sick for 5 days, so that’s a big win, right?! 👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼
